column1: "Be The Light" Round Car Coaster - Bulk
column4:
Our round car coasters will fit most cup holders and are made from absorbent stoneware. Will work for hot and cold beverages and absorb spills and condensation. These are designed, printed and packaged in the USA. Our bulk packed car coasters will come individually bubble wrapped with a UPC sticker on the back. Work best with the counter top display 70001.

Also available in packaged form Item #CC73296
